title: Welcome to the GitRepo Printer bot!
message:
With this bot you can print files that are on github, with the specific link.

You can use the flag `--format` to specify the markdown highlight

You can use the flag `--branch` to specify the branch that the file is in. Default is `master`

Example:
`?git github_user/repo_name/dir/file.c --branch test --format c`
